                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 36,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Arataki Itto_icon.png",
                      "name": "Arataki Itto",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Since Itto can convert DEF to ATK and deals Charge Attack DMG, he has low ATK requirements. Since this weapon increases Charge Attack DMG, this weapon is an ideal choice if other 4 or 5-star weapons are unavailable.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "name": "Xinyan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Once Xinyan unlocks C6, she can convert DEF to ATK and deals Charge Attack DMG. Therefore, this weapon is an ideal weapon at early stages.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
